{"pageProps":{"source":"<link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/CEk5c0i.jpg\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/PXVpcnT.jpg\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ktpFD4C.jpg\"/><div class=\"space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0\"><p><a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://store.dailystoic.com/collections/pendants/products/the-obstacle-is-the-way-pendant\">Le médaillon The Obstacle Is The Way de Ryan Holiday</a> provient d&#x27;une citation de l&#x27;un des pères du <strong>stoïcisme</strong> <strong>Marc Aurèle</strong> dans son livre &quot;<a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://amzn.to/36nC9q1\">Pensées pour moi-même</a>&quot;.</p><blockquote class=\"callout quote\">\n                    \n                        <div class=\"callout-title\">\n                            <div class=\"callout-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div>\n                            <div class=\"callout-title-inner\">Marc Aurèle - Pensées pour moi-même (Livre V chapitre XX)</div>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"callout-content\">\n                        <p>« The impediment to action advances action. What stands in the way becomes the way. »</p>\n                    </div>\n                </blockquote><p>Qui peut se traduire par : &quot;L&#x27;obstacle à l&#x27;action fait avancer l&#x27;action. Ce qui se trouve sur le chemin devient le chemin.&quot;</p><p>Ou plus précisément &quot;Ce qui nous empêche d’agir devient le motif de notre action, et ce qui nous barre la route devient ce vers quoi nous marchons.&quot;</p><p><strong>Les obstacles de la vie sont inévitables, au lieu de les éviter, mieux vaut les voir comme une opportunité.</strong></p><p>Une opportunité d&#x27;apprendre quelque chose et de mieux faire face aux défis futurs.</p><p>On ne contrôle pas le monde extérieur, mais on peut contrôler notre réaction.</p><p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CEk5c0i.jpg\" alt=\"|400\"/>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PXVpcnT.jpg\" alt=\"|400\"/>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ktpFD4C.jpg\" alt=\"|400\"/></p><blockquote class=\"callout quote\">\n                    \n                        <div class=\"callout-title\">\n                            <div class=\"callout-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div>\n                            <div class=\"callout-title-inner\">James Clear</div>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"callout-content\">\n                        <p>You cannot remove struggle from life, but you can improve your ability to handle challenge.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </blockquote><blockquote class=\"callout quote\">\n                    \n                        <div class=\"callout-title\">\n                            <div class=\"callout-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div>\n                            <div class=\"callout-title-inner\">Mark Manson</div>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"callout-content\">\n                        <p>Don’t hope for a life without problems, There’s no such thing. Instead, hope for a life full of good problems.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </blockquote><hr/><p>Références :</p><ul>\n<li><a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://amzn.to/3CGHPHG\">The Daily Stoic - Ryan Holiday</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://youtube.com/watch?v=CxUd2E5QvM8\">Daily Stoic - Marcus Aurelius&#x27; Most Influential Stoic Teaching</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://amzn.to/3L0y0Hk\">L&#x27;obstacle est le chemin - Ryan Holiday</a></li>\n<li>\n<a class=\"\" href=\"/stoicisme\">Stoïcisme</a>\n\n</li>\n</ul></div>","isIndex":false,"file":"Mon pendentif.md","fileName":"Mon pendentif","title":"Signification du pendentif \"The Obstacle Is the Way\" de Ryan Holiday","comments":true,"permalink":"signification-pendentif-obstacle-is-the-way","datePublished":"2022-03-11T12:00","dateUpdated":"2022-03-11T12:00","publish":true,"rss":true},"__N_SSG":true}